Class Application

java.lang.Object
model.Application
public class Application extends Object
Represents a flat booking application submitted by an Applicant.

Tracks the applicant, project, chosen unit type, application status, and timestamp of submission.

Since:
24/4/2025
Version:
final
Author:
FCSH Group 2
